text: Fauji Foundation Model School Adyala Road or Fauji Foundation Model School Adyala Road Campus is a branch of model schools established across the country by Fuji Foundation.https://education.fauji.org.pk/history , Retrieved 9 June 2017 https://www.fui.edu.pk/sites/default/files/1660448831879_compressed.pdf It is located at Adyala Road Rawalpindi. The school was established on 3 April 1998. ==References== Category:Education in Pakistan Category:Schools
